author: Russell Brand
description:
Is this Superman... Super-Trump? Russell breaks down James Gunn’s new trailer and what it says about America in the post-Trump era. With themes of masculinity, illegal immigration, power, and identity, this Superman isn’t just saving the world—he’s confronting the culture war. Is this a sly appeal to MAGA bros, a critique of modern liberalism, or both?
